# Source-distribution (sdist) contents - defense-in-depth.
#
# The wheel already excludes everything outside the production packages via
# [tool.setuptools.packages.find] in pyproject.toml (include = controller*,
# model*, utils*, view*, src*). The sdist, however, is built from MANIFEST/SCM
# rather than packages.find, so without these prunes dev/test/doc trees would
# ride along. In particular `scripts/` contains the CUA sign-off harness, which
# drives the real keyboard/mouse via pyautogui and must never be distributed.
prune scripts
prune test_scripts
prune docs
prune .codegraph
